Use the menu bar 'edit' to copy , cut , past , undo , redo.

Use the menu file to save the current file , have a new file , open a file.

Look at the console to see the actions performed.

click on the buttons "set borne a " and "set borne b" to set
the selection born at the current pos of the cursor in the textBox.

Use the insert button to insert whatever there is in the textBox beneath